        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\n&#39; 1. 全局排版与高颜值样式配置，去掉标题\ntop to bottom direction\nskinparam classAttributeIconSize 0\nskinparam packageStyle rectangle\nskinparam shadowing false\nskinparam noteBackgroundColor white\nskinparam noteBorderColor black\nskinparam noteFontColor black\nskinparam noteTextAlignment left\n\n&#39; 2. 核心紧凑黑科技（强行压缩间距）\nskinparam ranksep 25\nskinparam nodesep 30\n\n&#39; ==========================================\n&#39; 定义类（保留完整定义）\n&#39; ==========================================\nclass SchedulingEngine &lt;&lt;controller&gt;&gt; {\n  - globalBudget\n  - allocationPolicy\n  + allocateBudget()\n  + updatePolicy()\n}\n\n&#39; 3. 在 together 块中对调位置：StratifiedUnit 放最前，SampleGenerator 放中间\n&#39; 这比用 hidden 线靠谱得多，不会产生多余的幽灵空间\ntogether {\n  class StratifiedUnit &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt; {\n    - unitId\n    - stateSummary\n    - feedbackStats\n    + updateStats()\n    + recordFeedback()\n  }\n\n  class SampleGenerator &lt;&lt;service&gt;&gt; {\n    - generationTemplate\n    - generationConfig\n    + generateSample()\n    + generateBatch()\n  }\n}\n\nclass RefinementEngine &lt;&lt;service&gt;&gt; {\n  - refinementRules\n  - dedupStrategy\n  + refineSample()\n  + refineBatch()\n}\n\nclass TrainingPool &lt;&lt;repository&gt;&gt; {\n  - acceptedSamples\n  - sampleIndex\n  + appendSample()\n  + fetchSamples()\n}\n\n&#39; ==========================================\n&#39; 4. 核心布局导引 (Layout Guides)\n&#39; 这一步是实现 V型紧凑 + 水平流水线的关键。\n&#39; ==========================================\n\n&#39; 让 SchedulingEngine 居中在顶部 rank\nSchedulingEngine -[hidden]d- StratifiedUnit\nSchedulingEngine -[hidden]d- SampleGenerator\n\n&#39; 核心：通过 hidden 线强制左右顺序——StratifiedUnit 在左，SampleGenerator 在中（在同一 rank 上）\n&#39; 这彻底解决了交叉问题\nStratifiedUnit -[hidden]r- SampleGenerator\n\n&#39; 核心流水线布局导引：Generator 之后水平向右排布\nSampleGenerator -[hidden]r- RefinementEngine\nRefinementEngine -[hidden]r- TrainingPool\n\n&#39; ==========================================\n&#39; 5. 关系连线 (根据布局导引流动)\n&#39; 使用 `-r-&gt;` 强制流水线水平流动，巧用 `\\n` 换行防止线条拉长\n&#39; ==========================================\n\n&#39; 核心控制器的向下分支\nSchedulingEngine \&quot;1\&quot; -d-&gt; \&quot;*\&quot; StratifiedUnit : 管理\\n更新状态\nSchedulingEngine ..d.&gt; SampleGenerator : 调度\\n条件合成\n\n&#39; 水平数据流水线（通过 `-r-` 指令强制向右）\nSampleGenerator ..r.&gt; RefinementEngine : 输出\\n候选样本\nRefinementEngine -r-&gt; TrainingPool : 写入通过\\n精炼的样本\n\n&#39; ==========================================\n&#39; 6. 注释 (Notes)\n&#39; 将注释放在 RefinementEngine 的上方，不会干扰水平线条。\n&#39; ==========================================\nnote top of RefinementEngine\n  依赖执行验证模块返回的验证结果\n  用于过滤、去重、清洗与一致性检查\nend note\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="qv1WagnDIQbfAjHOOneH-63">
